description: This is the Xray Test Issue Type. Used to define test cases of different types that can be executed multiple times using Test Execution issues.
name: Test

description: This is the Xray Test Set Issue Type. Creates a group of test cases. Used to associate all included Tests with other Xray issue types like Test Execution and Test Plan. A Test Set can also be associated with a requirement issue to provide coverage and test status.
name: Test Set

description: This is the Xray Test Plan Issue Type. Used to define the scope of test cases for a given test campaign and to aggregate all executions for those tests displaying the latest result for each test case.
name: Test Plan

description: This is the Xray Test Execution Issue Type. Used to execute test cases already defined.
name: Test Execution

description: This is the Xray Precondition Issue Type. Used to abstract common actions that must be ensured before the test case execution. A Precondition can be associated with multiple test cases.
name: Precondition

description: This is the Xray Sub Test Execution Issue Type. Used to execute test cases already defined. A Sub Test Execution can be created for a parent issue like a requirement in order to execute the test cases associated with it.
name: Sub Test Execution
